author: @ejmotta
content: bunch of nonsense to say there were 1.5MM there @ Copacabana. The crowd was around an area of 182 x 620 meters = 112.000 square meters, so on a 5 person per square meter would give approx 560K people, let's say we have a 15% error on measurement of the area, so that would give around 650K people attending. Good number, but very far away from a misleading 1.5MM #
